  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for the Peace and Security Funders Group to (re-) define peace and security philanthropy&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;The Peace and Security Funders Group (PSFG), operating under the aegis of the Fund for Constitutional Government, is an association of donors dedicated to fostering effective philanthropy in the area of peace and security. As PSFG works to provide its philanthropist members a base of information to help guide their grantmaking, it has recognized the need to clarify the contours and diversity of such a wide-ranging field. This grant will be used to develop a comprehensive map of peace and security philanthropy &#x2014; including a breakdown of subfields, analysis of trends, and an interactive website &#x2014; to help donors place themselves within the broader effort and enable PSFG to bring new funders into the field.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
